{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011EtSJA2Bb7ScPk3WY9mFkq","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→@flow-discovery\n     2→Feature: Flow discovery\n     3→  The CLI enumerates built-in flow presets and shows their stage sequences.\n     4→\n     5→  @flow-list-all-presets\n     6→  Scenario: list all presets\n     7→    When I run \"ralph-burning flow list\"\n     8→    Then the output should include \"standard\"\n     9→    And the output should include \"quick_dev\"\n    10→    And the output should include \"docs_change\"\n    11→    And the output should include \"ci_improvement\"\n    12→\n    13→  @flow-show-each-preset\n    14→  Scenario Outline: show each preset\n    15→    When I run \"ralph-burning flow show <flow_id>\"\n    16→    Then the output should include \"Stage count\"\n    17→    And the output should include \"<stage_1>\"\n    18→    And the command should exit successfully\n    19→\n    20→    Examples:\n    21→      | flow_id        | stage_1            |\n    22→      | standard       | prompt_review      |\n    23→      | quick_dev      | plan_and_implement |\n    24→      | docs_change    | docs_plan          |\n    25→      | ci_improvement | ci_plan            |\n    26→\n    27→  @flow-show-invalid-preset\n    28→  Scenario: show invalid preset\n    29→    When I run \"ralph-burning flow show unknown_flow\"\n    30→    Then the command should fail with a clear invalid-flow error\n    31→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01GmHc9N8Srjnat2yn1mzYfx","session_id":"216e97eb-aa57-41df-a04f-9831b7c2815e","uuid":"7c620ead-13b0-458e-980c-ce091591d1e8"}
